name: Track Uniform
description:
Greetings

This is a Lora model trained on the track uniform.

Edit.

Adding track uniform to the prompt would be a nice touch. taking your choice.

IMPORTANT !

  1. Strength of 0.8~0.9 is good.

  2. I recommend adding "navel" separately from the trigger word.

If you really like it, please consider a small donation.

The donated money will be used to pay for electricity.

modelVersions.name: v1.5
modelVersions.description:
I edited training images and change captions.

I think it is now easier to match with other character lora.
